	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I agree that sticking to certain limits does not necessary mean someone wants to &quot;role-play&quot;.<br />On the one hand, I'm also developing with a small cart in mind, but that's because I want it to be easy and cheap to build a real cart, and I also don't have a budget to hire someone to create graphics for me so I'd have no excuse for limited tilesets otherwise. On the other hand I also want to have a small game pushing certain aspects of the NES with little to no help coming from &quot;the outside&quot;. But I think I've done enough topic de-railing for a while now.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
