		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />MMC1 (wired as <a href="https://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/SxROM#Higher_CHR_lines" class="postlink">SXROM</a>) and FME-7 (wired as <a href="https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=9&amp;t=12467" class="postlink">loopy speculated and l_oliveira confirmed</a>) can also bankswitch $6000-$7FFF.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
